        "Four journalists of the Sirasa TV channel who went to cover the protests held in front of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe's private residence were brutally assaulted by Police Special Task Force officers.",
        "This inhuman attack has been done even while shouting, 'Please don't hit, sir, here are the attackers'."
